name: HAPPY 2022
description:
This NFT will be submitted to the Rocking New Year JACKPOT event host by myself, @rblbab and my co-hosts @TerosEso @brainksy @ninacrypto2 and @Erythric.  #HENjackpot on social media.

One edition of this NFT, (and all event NFTs) will be sent to the jackpot holding account, tz1MQWZJdnaWhuCkZ35WvjFh6j2k4oMhwByu.  The other 21 editions will be available for collecting starting December 28th 2021.  All the editions in the jackpot holding account will be awarded to one person who collects an event NFT on primary.  

Hope you will join in as an artist and/or as a collector.  Go to any host on Twitter for more information!
